Components are reusable pieces of UI
Most components are reusable pieces of the user interface, like buttons and menus. In Nuxt, you can create these components in the
directory, and they will be automatically available across your application without having to explicitly import them.
Pages are views tied to a specific route
Pages represent views for each specific route pattern. Every file in the
directory represents a different route displaying its content.
